title: Twitter could delete dormant profiles. Here’s how to save them.
description: Worried about old tweets from someone who has passed away? Here's how to save copies of them in case they are deleted.

title: Heather Armstrong, who made it okay to say motherhood was hard, dead at 47
description: Armstrong detailed her struggles with postpartum depression, her conflicted emotions about motherhood, her battles with alcoholism, and her relationship and eventual divorce.

title: Google is changing the way we search with AI. It could upend the web.
description: Google executives took the IO stage to tout their AI search tool, saying it would directly generate answers to some queries, a move publishers and bloggers dread.
